media:group.media:title: OpenBSD 7.2
media:group.media:description:
In this video I do a review of OpenBSD 7.2 which ads some support for new hardware (Apple M2 and Snapdragon 8cx Gen 3 processors) aswell as very old hardware like the luna 88k.  I also do an upgrade on my OpenBSD Bastion host.

Get yourself a cheap and secure OpenBSD bastion host, or any other VPS utility here.
